# hacker hive

## the idea

the hacker hive is project to make [prototype](http://seasteading.wpengine.netdna-cdn.com/files/research/governance/Friedman&Taylor_2011_Seasteading_APEE.pdf) [housing](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Northside,_Berkeley,_California) [cooperatives](http://www.bsc.coop/) started by the [UC Berkeley hacker community](http://hackersatberkeley.com/).

some of us hackers already live together. let's have all hackers live together as the hacker hive, making a larger community with added benefits while retaining our own sub-hives of roommates, friends, and family. anyone can join the hacker hive with infinitely recursive sub-hives.

